  <section>
    <h2>‚è∞ What is Apple Screen Time?</h2>

    <p>Apple Screen Time is a built-in feature on iPhone, iPad, and Mac that helps families manage device usage, set app limits, filter content, and monitor activity across all Apple devices.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
