      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3>‚è≥ App Limits</h3>
        <p>Set time limits for specific apps or app categories (Social Media, Games, Entertainment). Limits reset daily.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3>üåô Downtime</h3>
        <p>Schedule device-free time (bedtime, dinner, homework). Only allowed apps are accessible during downtime.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3>üîí Content Restrictions</h3>
        <p>Block explicit content, filter websites, restrict app downloads, and set age-appropriate content ratings.</p>
      </div>

