      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3>üîê Screen Time Passcode</h3>
        <p>Protect settings with a passcode so children cannot bypass restrictions or extend time limits.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-success">
      <strong>Built-In & Free:</strong> Screen Time is included with iOS, iPadOS, and macOS at no additional cost. Works seamlessly across all Apple devices.
